I should be excited.&nbsp; Counting today, I have two more days of work and then nearly a week&#39;s vacation.&nbsp; Oddly, though, I feel a strange sense of foreboding.&nbsp; I wonder why?

Yesterday&#39;s shift was wild, lots of tourists, etc.&nbsp; This was one of the strangest comments I got:&nbsp; &quot;What river are we near?&nbsp; The Rio Grande?&nbsp; Why do people around here think I should have heard of it?&quot;
So, before you knew me, had YOU heard of the Rio Grande?
